標準ライブラリを使う

int_to_mini_roman = 入力 number に対し {
   values=[1000,900,500,400,100,90,50,40,10,9,5,4,1]
   symbols=["m","cm","d","cd","c","xc","l","xl","x","ix","v","iv","i"]
   result=""
   i=0
   valuesの大きさ回くり返す{
      v=values[i]
      s=symbols[i]
      もしnumberがv以上ならば{
         q=商(number,v)
         q回くり返す{
            resultにsを追加する
         }
         number=剰余(number,v)
      }
      iを増やす
   }
   resultが答え
}